			  <!-- Text on the left -->
			  <div class="col-md-6">
				<h2>Dogs</h2>
				<p>I believe dogs are the absolute best animals in the world. They are known to do all sorts of jobs for us. They work for the police, help on farms, 
					assist the handicapped, help with hunting, in combat, and so much more. They love to play and can even be taught tricks. </p>
			  </div>
			  
			  <!-- Image on the right -->
